WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 15=

01:59.283 --> 02:00.242
Put it aside.

02:10.922 --> 02:12.123
What happened?

02:13.322 --> 02:15.403
A ghost!

02:15.922 --> 02:19.642
I fell into the pond.
Something grabbed my foot.

02:20.162 --> 02:22.243
Such great strength!
I couldn't shake it off at all.

02:22.843 --> 02:24.363
It's her!

02:24.363 --> 02:25.083
Shut up.

02:25.563 --> 02:28.003
In this world, there is no ghost.

02:28.363 --> 02:30.683
Don't talk nonsense here
and mislead people.

02:30.683 --> 02:32.683
It's true, Uncle Wending.
There really is a ghost.

02:32.683 --> 02:33.403
Alright.

02:33.722 --> 02:35.083
Ying, enough.

02:35.523 --> 02:37.042
You're just too terrified. Enough.

02:37.042 --> 02:38.683
You must be tangled by water plants.

02:38.683 --> 02:39.202
I...

02:49.803 --> 02:50.762
It's so late.

02:51.442 --> 02:54.683
Why weren't you two
resting in your rooms,

02:54.843 --> 02:56.762
but staying by the pond?

02:58.442 --> 02:59.882
I asked her to go.

03:00.523 --> 03:02.243
Although I took back Shende Shop,

03:02.523 --> 03:04.283
business hasn't picked up.

03:04.843 --> 03:06.523
I wanted to host a ladies' banquet,

03:06.563 --> 03:09.123
inviting the noble ladies
from all mansions

03:09.123 --> 03:10.832
in the capital to promote Shende Shop.

03:11.322 --> 03:13.752
She knows the preferences
of the noble ladies,

03:13.752 --> 03:15.602
so I asked her to help me host it.

03:16.123 --> 03:17.843
Host a banquet?

03:17.843 --> 03:22.403
When did you two become
so close and support each other?

03:25.123 --> 03:27.283
We are sisters connected by blood.

03:27.683 --> 03:29.523
And now both of us
have married a prince.

03:29.762 --> 03:32.162
We share honor and disgrace.

03:33.283 --> 03:36.042
If we don't support each other,
should we undermine each other,

03:36.042 --> 03:37.523
letting outsiders make fun of us?

03:38.283 --> 03:41.922
The color of this skeleton has faded.
This is definitely not a recent death.

03:42.882 --> 03:46.602
I'm afraid it's been
soaking in water for some years.

03:46.963 --> 03:49.482
Who is it exactly?

03:49.482 --> 03:52.882
- Yeah.
- When pulled out of the water,

03:53.363 --> 03:55.722
there were stones tied to this skeleton.

03:56.243 --> 03:58.202
No wonder it never floated up.

03:58.683 --> 04:01.963
This was intended to keep her
at the bottom of the water forever.

04:01.963 --> 04:03.243
Such an atrocity!

04:03.683 --> 04:07.202
This is clearly a murder case.

04:08.283 --> 04:11.083
In my opinion, we should report this
and let the officials investigate.

04:11.363 --> 04:14.322
What? Absurd!

04:14.623 --> 04:15.123
Well...

04:15.123 --> 04:18.882
This skeleton has been there for years.

04:18.882 --> 04:21.603
Is it that easy to investigate?

04:22.442 --> 04:26.563
Who knows what old stories
it might stir up?

04:26.642 --> 04:28.082
Listen, all of you.

04:28.363 --> 04:31.442
This matter ends here tonight.

04:31.842 --> 04:33.683
No more discussion.

04:34.043 --> 04:36.592
Do not spread a single word
outside the mansion.

04:36.848 --> 04:38.483
Do you hear me?

04:41.282 --> 04:44.363
Tonight, no one is allowed
to leave the mansion.

04:46.522 --> 04:49.163
Arrange for the elders to go rest.

04:49.322 --> 04:50.123
Yes.

04:50.882 --> 04:53.563
Then what should we do
with the skeleton?

04:53.563 --> 04:54.882
Go rest.

04:55.882 --> 04:58.642
The ancestors have blessings,
so naturally they are not afraid.

04:59.522 --> 05:03.563
But it's not certain
whether we can rest properly.

05:04.082 --> 05:05.842
After all, a tragic death
breeds resentment.

05:06.082 --> 05:10.483
What if something comes
to haunt us at midnight?

05:14.123 --> 05:15.003
She won't.

05:27.483 --> 05:30.762
She is Yanlu, my mother's
personal maid back then.

05:31.282 --> 05:33.282
Yanlu? Which Yanlu?

05:33.442 --> 05:35.603
There's such a maid in the mansion?

05:44.762 --> 05:46.483
Uncle Wending, don't you remember Yanlu?

05:46.563 --> 05:48.762
Back then, you broke into
my mother's courtyard

05:49.243 --> 05:50.483
and took her things.

05:51.163 --> 05:54.442
Yanlu was injured by you when she tried
to protect my mother's belongings.

05:55.163 --> 05:59.322
Later, your men carried her away,
saying they would treat her wounds.

05:59.683 --> 06:01.123
But now?

06:02.163 --> 06:03.243
She's dead.

06:04.442 --> 06:07.282
And her body was found in the pond
of our Ye family garden,

06:07.282 --> 06:08.563
even with stones tied to it.

06:08.563 --> 06:09.282
Shut up.

06:10.762 --> 06:14.082
How can you identify
a person from just bones?

06:14.683 --> 06:16.363
That's not Yanlu at all.

06:18.483 --> 06:19.762
I might not recognize her well,

06:21.483 --> 06:23.043
but I recognize this bracelet.

06:23.563 --> 06:27.043
This is what my mother
personally awarded her back then.

06:28.522 --> 06:32.043
When I was little, Yanlu often
took it off for me to play with.

06:32.842 --> 06:35.603
I remember
the twined branch pattern on it clearly.

06:36.923 --> 06:40.642
Tell me. Why did she die?

06:44.603 --> 06:46.123
Did you kill her?

06:48.043 --> 06:49.842
You not only caused my mother's death,

06:50.282 --> 06:53.282
but you also harmed a loyal maid
who protected my mother?

06:53.683 --> 06:59.563
Ridiculous! Your mother Xu Wanzhou
returned to Lishan Mountain with you.

06:59.962 --> 07:01.043
She's dead?

07:01.723 --> 07:03.043
She is already dead.

07:04.563 --> 07:06.163
Uncle Wending, do you really not know?

07:08.442 --> 07:11.483
Father, haven't you told him yet?

07:23.243 --> 07:24.522
She is already dead.

07:27.282 --> 07:29.202
And you are all murderers.

07:32.123 --> 07:36.322
Mo Xiuwen was already
a death-row prisoner at that time,

07:36.603 --> 07:38.962
a confirmed rebel.

07:39.123 --> 07:41.842
Your mother was just a woman,

07:42.282 --> 07:43.442
yet she's not well-behaved,

07:43.723 --> 07:49.202
and colluded with a court rebel
like Mo Xiuwen,

07:49.642 --> 07:52.003
attempting to stir up trouble

07:52.522 --> 07:55.043
and dragging
the entire Ye family into it.

07:55.563 --> 07:58.483
Did she want us
to be buried with that rebel?

07:59.243 --> 08:05.082
The Ye family cast her out,
to cut our losses and seek survival.

08:05.402 --> 08:09.563
It was not only to save the lives
of our clan, over a hundred people,

08:10.043 --> 08:12.043
but also to give her a way out.

08:15.842 --> 08:16.723
A way out?

08:20.322 --> 08:21.803
Is that what you think too, Father?

08:26.442 --> 08:28.163
Did you really do that for her sake?

08:30.163 --> 08:31.882
But right after
Lishan Academy sealed off,

08:32.642 --> 08:35.243
you were afraid of being implicated
and forced her to leave.

08:37.323 --> 08:40.003
Even when she was on her deathbed,
breathing her last.

08:40.603 --> 08:42.603
Did you ever care about her?

08:45.603 --> 08:46.103
Mom!

08:48.443 --> 08:49.703
Mom!

08:50.042 --> 08:51.162
Mom, hang in there.

08:51.162 --> 08:51.723
General Mo.

08:51.723 --> 08:52.843
Mom, don't scare me.

08:52.843 --> 08:53.963
I'm sorry.

08:54.282 --> 08:54.963
Mom.

08:55.642 --> 08:56.443
My lady.

08:57.642 --> 08:58.642
Stop the carriage.

09:00.162 --> 09:01.282
Physician, please hurry!

09:01.282 --> 09:02.123
Slow down.

09:06.083 --> 09:06.723
Mom.

09:10.603 --> 09:14.723
Because she was too out of touch
to see the situation clearly.

09:15.203 --> 09:17.963
The Empress Dowager
has long had absolute power.

09:18.083 --> 09:19.162
But what about you?

09:19.483 --> 09:23.882
Lishan Academy sealed off the mountain
under the pretext of compiling texts,

09:24.522 --> 09:25.882
offending the current emperor.

09:25.882 --> 09:27.443
So you killed Yanlu?

09:27.723 --> 09:30.282
Nonsense! I didn't.

09:30.282 --> 09:31.882
You pushed her into the water.

09:31.882 --> 09:32.642
Nonsense!

09:34.443 --> 09:38.003
We hired a physician
to save her back then.

09:38.162 --> 09:40.802
She died of severe injuries.

09:40.882 --> 09:43.723
She's destined to have a short life.
You can't blame us for that.

09:44.802 --> 09:45.642
What?

09:47.123 --> 09:48.363
Well said.

09:49.963 --> 09:51.603
Even if she really died of her injuries,

09:52.522 --> 09:53.963
but the Ye family

09:54.083 --> 09:56.323
could not even spare a thin coffin
and a handful of earth

09:56.323 --> 09:57.682
for her?

10:04.483 --> 10:07.042
Her body sank to the bottom
of the pool in the garden,

10:07.802 --> 10:09.363
even with stones tied to it.

10:10.522 --> 10:12.762
If you did nothing wrong,
why would this happen?

10:12.762 --> 10:13.562
You!

10:16.123 --> 10:20.762
You tell me. Was it you
who buried her back then?

10:21.723 --> 10:24.323
Master Wending, it's me.

10:24.802 --> 10:27.723
I buried her. I did bury her!

10:28.123 --> 10:32.203
Well, maybe Ms. Xu and the maid
truly have resentment

10:32.802 --> 10:35.603
- and they've come back to seek justice.
- Come on, don't talk nonsense!

10:35.603 --> 10:38.843
Wanzhou. It must be Wanzhou.

10:40.123 --> 10:42.483
She and Yanlu are blaming us.

10:42.483 --> 10:44.123
They're blaming us.

10:44.603 --> 10:45.802
D-Don't come for us.

10:46.483 --> 10:49.123
D-Don't come for me!

10:49.123 --> 10:49.882
Enough nonsense!

10:50.603 --> 10:51.522
Don't come for me!

10:51.522 --> 10:52.642
Stop this nonsense!

10:52.882 --> 10:54.003
They're dead.

10:54.003 --> 10:54.723
Don't come for me!

10:54.723 --> 10:55.723
Stop it now, or I'll...

10:55.723 --> 10:56.885
Master, something's happened.

10:56.885 --> 11:00.003
Jingzhao Prefecture is searching
the entire capital for some fugitives.

11:00.443 --> 11:01.642
How could this happen?

11:02.083 --> 11:04.083
What is wrong with tonight?

11:17.162 --> 11:21.922
♪The towering Lishan Mountain♪

11:24.003 --> 11:29.162
♪Rises into the sky♪

11:31.642 --> 11:36.042
♪The mighty Lishui River♪

11:37.802 --> 11:40.603
♪Flows ever east♪

11:40.603 --> 11:41.882
Who is playing the guqin there?

11:42.243 --> 11:45.443
It's Wanzhou. Wanzhou is back!

11:46.162 --> 11:48.282
She's back.

11:49.083 --> 11:49.922
You go check.

11:49.922 --> 11:51.083
I'm not going.

11:51.483 --> 11:53.922
Let me see who's playing tricks.

11:53.922 --> 11:55.483
Come on, let's go together.

11:55.483 --> 11:56.042
No way.

11:56.042 --> 11:56.802
I'm not going.

11:56.802 --> 11:57.562
Let's go.

11:57.562 --> 11:58.203
I'm not going.

11:58.203 --> 11:59.123
Hurry, Father.

11:59.123 --> 11:59.723
I'm not going.

11:59.723 --> 12:00.642
- No, no!
- Hurry!

12:00.642 --> 12:02.562
No. I don't want to go!

12:02.562 --> 12:05.642
Don't push me. I don't want to go.

12:10.123 --> 12:10.922
I'm not going.

12:11.522 --> 12:12.682
- Don't be scared.
- I don't want to go.

12:13.402 --> 12:14.522
What are you afraid of?

12:15.203 --> 12:15.922
I...

12:16.464 --> 12:18.864
- There's no ghost in the world.
- I'm not going.

12:18.864 --> 12:20.042
Don't come for me.

12:22.003 --> 12:22.562
I'm not going.

12:22.562 --> 12:23.402
This way.

12:29.642 --> 12:32.402
You wench! Are you
trying to scare us to death?

12:34.843 --> 12:36.802
My lady, I have no idea.

12:37.562 --> 12:40.642
I think I fell asleep and woke up here.

12:41.402 --> 12:42.963
This guqin...

12:43.443 --> 12:45.162
It must be this guqin haunting.

12:53.323 --> 12:54.203
My lady.

12:58.123 --> 12:59.003
Wenhua.

13:02.243 --> 13:03.363
Long time no see.

13:05.522 --> 13:06.483
How are you?

13:08.162 --> 13:10.203
Why didn't you help me back then?

13:10.703 --> 13:11.203
Stay back.

13:11.203 --> 13:12.123
Why?

13:12.123 --> 13:12.843
Stay back.

13:13.203 --> 13:14.642
Give it back.

13:14.642 --> 13:15.922
- Stay back.
- I'm going back to Lishan Mountain.

13:15.922 --> 13:17.042
Away, evil spirits!

13:19.522 --> 13:23.162
Master, save me!

13:23.642 --> 13:25.562
Master, save me!

13:26.736 --> 13:27.907
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

13:32.003 --> 13:34.323
Open the door! Hurry! Open up!

13:35.083 --> 13:36.963
Open the door! Open up! Hurry!

13:36.963 --> 13:39.536
(Meng's Incense and Candle Shop)

13:46.123 --> 13:48.003
Your Highness, are you all right?

13:53.723 --> 13:54.323
Your Highness.

13:55.723 --> 13:56.963
You shouldn't come to save me.

13:57.522 --> 14:00.363
So I should just watch
you guys get captured?

14:01.323 --> 14:03.723
Your Highness, my life is worthless.

14:03.723 --> 14:06.162
If I can't break out,
I'll just end myself.

14:06.323 --> 14:07.762
How could I let you take risks?

14:07.963 --> 14:10.843
All these years,
you've been loyal to me.

14:11.522 --> 14:13.603
I can't let anyone else
around me get hurt anymore.

14:13.882 --> 14:14.682
Besides,

14:15.603 --> 14:17.562
our plan has just begun.

14:19.762 --> 14:20.562
I know.

14:21.443 --> 14:23.723
Your Highness,
the entire city is on high alert now.

14:23.802 --> 14:24.944
All the wards are isolated.

14:24.944 --> 14:26.768
The wardens are conducting
a thorough search.

14:26.768 --> 14:28.243
If we can't go back before dawn,

14:28.522 --> 14:29.963
they'll find us sooner or later.

14:38.123 --> 14:43.443
Wending, this is my fault.
Please, everyone, go back and rest.

14:43.483 --> 14:44.802
Get some rest.

14:47.922 --> 14:48.723
Get rest.

14:58.562 --> 15:01.104
I noticed that the evil aura here
is overwhelming

15:01.104 --> 15:03.042
and calculated
that disaster would strike here,

15:03.682 --> 15:06.042
so I came one day early.

15:07.042 --> 15:08.922
I hope I'm not disturbing you.

15:09.882 --> 15:12.922
No. Master, you've come just in time.

15:13.843 --> 15:17.963
Master, evil spirits
have invaded this place.

15:18.843 --> 15:20.003
You saw it too, right?

15:20.042 --> 15:22.922
My wife and all the servants
in the mansion have been possessed.

15:24.243 --> 15:26.162
Master, please save me!

15:27.243 --> 15:30.416
Have you finished folding
the 999 paper golden lotuses

15:30.416 --> 15:32.083
I asked you to?

15:32.402 --> 15:34.723
All done, not a single one missing.

15:34.802 --> 15:35.603
Good.

15:36.843 --> 15:39.363
Then I will set up
a ritual ground for you

15:39.603 --> 15:43.243
to send this uninvited guest
off your mansion.

15:43.603 --> 15:45.762
Heaven's gate opens, Earth's gate opens.

15:46.003 --> 15:47.963
Cinnabar cracks talismans
to startle demons.

15:47.963 --> 15:50.843
Bronze bells shake souls
to subdue the stiff corpses.

16:05.083 --> 16:06.282
The ritual is complete,

16:06.522 --> 16:08.083
but the spirit of the deceased lingers

16:08.562 --> 16:09.843
for a reason.

16:10.003 --> 16:15.123
She might have unfulfilled wishes
in the mortal world.

16:15.562 --> 16:16.483
Mr. Ye.

16:17.203 --> 16:19.243
I presume you know

16:19.323 --> 16:24.642
what this female guest in your mansion
cared about the most when she was alive.

16:29.802 --> 16:34.642
Mr. Ye, do you have anything
you wish to say to your wife?

16:38.483 --> 16:41.123
Give me back
the imperial decree, Wenhua.

16:41.123 --> 16:43.443
We promised General Mo, Wenhua.

16:43.802 --> 16:45.162
Father will be here soon.

16:45.162 --> 16:45.723
Wanzhou.

16:45.843 --> 16:46.363
Wenhua.

16:46.363 --> 16:49.723
I'm sorry for that. I'm sorry.

16:50.203 --> 16:52.963
Wenhua, who sent you here?

16:55.522 --> 16:56.323
I...

16:58.603 --> 16:59.762
I...

17:02.162 --> 17:03.882
I understand it's hard

17:03.882 --> 17:06.082
to speak out your mind.

17:06.723 --> 17:08.042
When you feel like it,

17:08.643 --> 17:09.762
you can pour them out

17:10.163 --> 17:11.522
through the brush.

18:18.683 --> 18:20.203
Past events and old grudges,

18:20.643 --> 18:22.203
all given to this flame.

19:09.522 --> 19:10.483
Don't be sad.

19:14.683 --> 19:15.802
I'm not sad.

19:18.883 --> 19:19.683
My lady.

19:22.602 --> 19:23.562
Don't be afraid.

19:55.683 --> 19:56.562
My lady.

20:40.003 --> 20:40.802
Come on.

20:42.282 --> 20:45.003
General Wang is a man of honor.

20:45.683 --> 20:47.522
As long as he doesn't
cause trouble for me,

20:47.842 --> 20:49.122
(Jingzhao Prefecture)
I'll let it go.

20:55.883 --> 20:57.522
The weather has changed.

21:06.243 --> 21:09.282
Your Highness, we've checked
several streets around.

21:09.762 --> 21:12.762
Now, only the Ye Mansion
remains unchecked.

21:15.243 --> 21:16.042
Ye Mansion.

21:21.730 --> 21:24.336
(Ye Mansion)

21:27.562 --> 21:32.963
(Mom, let's not go back to the capital.
Can we just stay in Lishan Mountain?)

21:33.562 --> 21:36.282
No, Li. You are
a child of the Ye family.

21:36.322 --> 21:38.963
And I am your father's lawful wife.

21:39.483 --> 21:43.562
Mom, why did you marry Father back then?

21:44.122 --> 21:45.802
Because I love your father.

21:46.483 --> 21:48.403
And does Father love you?

21:48.562 --> 21:49.802
Of course.

21:50.322 --> 21:53.562
Father loves me, and he loves you too.

22:25.082 --> 22:26.923
Who? Who's there?

22:30.963 --> 22:33.042
Someone! Someone come!

22:33.562 --> 22:34.403
Guards!

22:37.562 --> 22:39.362
Wanzhou, listen to me.

22:39.362 --> 22:43.042
I know I did something wrong,
but I had no choice.

22:43.403 --> 22:47.562
Wanzhou, you can't blame me.

22:47.562 --> 22:49.243
You forced me to do so.

22:49.683 --> 22:51.562
You insisted on holding onto that thing.

22:52.562 --> 22:54.322
I did it for the Ye family.

23:29.923 --> 23:32.723
Wanzhou, please spare me.

23:34.683 --> 23:36.122
I'm sorry.

23:36.403 --> 23:40.003
Please, forgive me.

23:42.403 --> 23:46.602
Please, I beg you.

23:51.003 --> 23:53.562
Li.

23:57.602 --> 23:58.403
Mom.

23:59.003 --> 24:00.122
What did you say?

24:00.483 --> 24:01.562
Mom, you're here.

24:02.122 --> 24:03.683
Who are you talking to?

24:06.122 --> 24:07.243
Who's there?

24:11.082 --> 24:11.883
Mom.

24:22.243 --> 24:23.723
Wanzhou.

24:32.163 --> 24:33.243
She's asking you something.

24:33.683 --> 24:34.643
She's asking you.

24:35.522 --> 24:37.584
The decree mobilizing
Heiyun Cavalry to the capital,

24:37.584 --> 24:38.802
who did you give it to?

24:39.362 --> 24:41.362
I...

24:45.362 --> 24:47.842
Dowager Consort Qin.

25:07.562 --> 25:08.842
I knew it.

25:09.163 --> 25:12.243
You and your short-lived mom
are cut from the same cloth.

25:12.403 --> 25:16.003
You're both vengeful spirits
crawling out of the underworld,

25:16.443 --> 25:18.602
coming to bring disaster
upon our Ye family.

25:19.362 --> 25:21.203
You've been faking it all along.

25:22.403 --> 25:24.082
So you are not senile

25:24.923 --> 25:25.802
and forget everything.

25:27.122 --> 25:29.362
I may forget everything,

25:30.723 --> 25:33.842
except the two of you,
mother and daughter.

25:34.362 --> 25:39.362
You jinx, you were born
to ruin the Ye family.

25:40.842 --> 25:41.683
Jinx?

25:42.163 --> 25:44.003
If Mom hadn't married him,

25:44.842 --> 25:46.963
he was just a low-ranking
ninth-grade official.

25:47.443 --> 25:49.963
His household couldn't
even afford a few servants.

25:50.522 --> 25:54.562
It was my mom's dowry
that made your Ye family prosperous.

25:55.003 --> 25:58.448
She tacitly allowed the Ye family
to use Lishan Mountain's name

25:58.448 --> 25:59.683
to pull strings.

25:59.683 --> 26:01.802
Only then did Ye Wenhua
and Ye Wending get promoted.

26:03.243 --> 26:06.082
Have you all forgotten this?

26:06.082 --> 26:06.883
Shut up.

26:07.923 --> 26:09.762
Since she married into the Ye family,

26:09.762 --> 26:12.243
she is a Ye in life
and a ghost of Ye in death.

26:12.243 --> 26:16.082
Her life should have been used
to support the Ye family.

26:16.562 --> 26:19.443
What you said was exactly
what she should have done.

26:20.122 --> 26:24.122
She should have lived
by the Ye family's rules,

26:24.403 --> 26:25.562
but she refused.

26:26.122 --> 26:29.122
She showed no respect
for her mother-in-law or her elders.

26:29.203 --> 26:33.562
What's worse, she wanted
to invite even greater trouble.

26:33.562 --> 26:34.842
But she left.

26:36.082 --> 26:38.203
She signed a divorce agreement

26:38.203 --> 26:39.842
and cut all ties with your Ye family.

26:39.883 --> 26:41.522
Why couldn't you let her leave?

26:42.562 --> 26:43.362
Leave?

26:45.802 --> 26:47.443
She never left.

26:48.483 --> 26:50.883
She was hiding at Zhengyi Temple
on the capital outskirts,

26:51.723 --> 26:52.842
refusing to leave.

26:53.362 --> 26:55.243
I know what you're up to.

26:55.243 --> 26:56.802
You still wanted to come back.

26:57.282 --> 26:59.802
She still wanted to seduce
Wenhua with her charm.

27:00.003 --> 27:05.243
You wanted to drag the Ye family down
to the underworld as your scapegoat.

27:06.403 --> 27:10.483
How could I let you go?
And how could I let her live?

27:12.842 --> 27:13.562
So,

27:15.282 --> 27:16.723
you killed her?

27:17.562 --> 27:19.562
So what if I did?

27:42.723 --> 27:46.163
It's only natural and proper for me
to clean up the mess from my family.

27:48.683 --> 27:52.403
Now, let's settle this debt.

28:20.784 --> 28:22.923
(Ye Mansion)

28:22.923 --> 28:24.562
Open up!

28:30.322 --> 28:32.443
We are Jingzhao Prefecture.
Search separately!

28:38.963 --> 28:39.463
Stop.

29:05.322 --> 29:06.802
(Mom,)

29:06.802 --> 29:10.203
when will the tree we planted grow up?

29:11.883 --> 29:15.602
When you grow up, it will shelter you
from the wind and rain.

29:25.443 --> 29:26.762
Guards!

29:27.359 --> 29:28.916
Guards!

29:43.082 --> 29:44.042
Li!

29:48.880 --> 29:49.808
No.

29:50.243 --> 29:51.122
Murder!

29:51.122 --> 29:54.302
Li! Li! Li!

29:58.842 --> 30:00.963
Murder!

30:01.522 --> 30:02.243
Li!

30:07.593 --> 30:08.313
No!

30:10.203 --> 30:11.003
No!

30:16.522 --> 30:17.163
No!

30:17.163 --> 30:17.683
No!

30:21.522 --> 30:22.562
No!

30:23.443 --> 30:24.322
Murder!

30:24.322 --> 30:25.322
Li, no!

30:25.322 --> 30:26.203
Murder!

30:27.042 --> 30:27.723
Li!

30:28.362 --> 30:29.243
Murder!

30:32.883 --> 30:36.163
No!

30:36.483 --> 30:38.282
Li, my legs hurt so much!

30:39.243 --> 30:40.963
Come and help me.

30:43.042 --> 30:45.122
Don't kill...

30:45.362 --> 30:46.802
Don't kill me!

31:08.802 --> 31:09.522
Li.

31:33.683 --> 31:34.243
Li.

31:35.643 --> 31:36.443
It's okay.

31:40.203 --> 31:41.042
It's okay.

32:16.883 --> 32:17.762
Get in the carriage.

32:26.522 --> 32:29.163
Your Highness,
the fish may have slipped away.

32:39.282 --> 32:39.923
Let's go.

33:20.643 --> 33:21.562
Physician, take care.

33:21.723 --> 33:22.483
Farewell.

33:34.282 --> 33:36.403
Mom.

33:36.643 --> 33:39.443
I am Wenshen. I'm back.

33:40.163 --> 33:41.322
I'm back.

33:44.483 --> 33:45.403
The physician says

33:46.483 --> 33:47.762
your wound is fine

33:49.203 --> 33:50.562
and you will be fine soon.

33:51.923 --> 33:52.963
When you recover,

33:53.483 --> 33:55.923
I'll take you to the Immortal Dwelling.

33:56.723 --> 33:58.802
They say it's where immortals live.

33:59.522 --> 34:04.042
The stream water is like colorful glass,

34:05.243 --> 34:06.562
extremely beautiful.

34:41.803 --> 34:43.763
Why are you here?

35:00.283 --> 35:01.082
Your Highness.

35:03.403 --> 35:05.682
Your Highness, don't you
have anything to ask me?

35:06.003 --> 35:08.122
If I ask, will you tell me the truth?

35:08.963 --> 35:10.202
Her Highness told me

35:10.202 --> 35:12.923
to answer truthfully
to any question you ask.

35:15.082 --> 35:16.242
What if I don't ask?

35:35.122 --> 35:37.162
Porridge. Hot porridge.

35:37.162 --> 35:39.283
Hot porridge with dates and chestnuts.

36:01.483 --> 36:02.283
Your Highness.

36:03.923 --> 36:05.443
Her Highness has great stamina.

36:05.923 --> 36:07.403
She's been out running recently.

36:07.602 --> 36:09.202
It is already the eighth lap for today.

36:09.483 --> 36:11.283
I told you to keep an eye
on the Ye family.

36:11.283 --> 36:13.122
Any abnormalities these past few days?

36:13.682 --> 36:16.283
Madam Ye is ill. It must be serious.

36:16.602 --> 36:18.562
The children from out of town
have all returned.

36:24.763 --> 36:25.963
Her Highness has gone back.

36:27.522 --> 36:28.363
Go.

36:36.363 --> 36:38.403
Your Highness,
you're finally back! You...

36:41.722 --> 36:45.003
Your Highness! Your Highness, terrible!

36:47.602 --> 36:48.403
Your Highness.

36:49.008 --> 36:51.003
White banners are hung
in front of the Ye Mansion.

36:51.003 --> 36:52.562
Madam Ye has passed away.

36:57.562 --> 36:58.602
Li, are you there?

36:59.682 --> 37:00.283
Yes.

37:12.483 --> 37:15.122
Your Highness, why are you here?
What's the matter?

37:21.283 --> 37:22.323
What happened?

37:32.763 --> 37:34.042
Your grandmother has passed.

37:38.522 --> 37:41.003
Since she got hit by a tree
on her birthday,

37:41.722 --> 37:43.122
she has been bedridden.

37:43.522 --> 37:45.072
Her condition deteriorated last night.

37:45.803 --> 37:46.923
After suffering all night,

37:47.923 --> 37:49.323
she still couldn't make it.

37:53.323 --> 37:54.803
I need to go back to the Ye Mansion.

37:55.283 --> 37:57.483
You have trouble walking. Please stay.

37:57.648 --> 37:59.344
I'll have our sister-in-law
accompany me.

38:00.363 --> 38:01.443
You'll go to her funeral?

38:01.602 --> 38:02.602
Of course.

38:03.363 --> 38:04.763
She's my grandmother,

38:05.003 --> 38:06.162
my close kin.

38:07.363 --> 38:08.682
We are bound by blood.

38:09.082 --> 38:11.722
Now she's passed away.
How can I be absent?

38:13.776 --> 38:15.242
The funeral must be taken seriously.

38:16.122 --> 38:17.923
I need to bring more things back.

38:20.602 --> 38:22.082
Incense, paper money, candles,

38:23.283 --> 38:24.682
seasonal fruits,

38:26.003 --> 38:27.443
wine, tea,

38:30.323 --> 38:32.082
and some flowers for the spirit tablet.

38:32.403 --> 38:33.522
All must be prepared.

38:35.202 --> 38:36.323
And eternal lamps.

38:36.562 --> 38:38.162
Nine lamps are suitable.

38:39.003 --> 38:42.003
But I wonder
where to buy them at this hour.

38:43.803 --> 38:45.562
Qingyu!

38:46.562 --> 38:47.522
Qingyu!

38:50.096 --> 38:55.024
(Ye Mansion)

38:55.024 --> 39:00.611
(Sacred Tablet
of the Late Mother, Ye Cenying)

39:22.883 --> 39:24.162
Why hasn't Ye Li come yet?

39:24.162 --> 39:25.648
Did you send someone to inform her?

39:26.963 --> 39:29.042
Why told her to come back?

39:29.363 --> 39:30.803
She's nothing but a jinx.

39:31.082 --> 39:33.360
Ever since she returned
from Lishan Mountain,

39:33.360 --> 39:36.122
Mother has been delirious,

39:36.162 --> 39:37.923
and even doesn't recognize us anymore.

39:38.722 --> 39:42.803
She's the one who caused Mother's death,
committing the heinous crime.

39:43.443 --> 39:44.562
If she returns,

39:44.763 --> 39:47.522
I will open the ancestral hall
and get the punishment rod.

39:51.082 --> 39:51.803
Master Wending.

39:51.803 --> 39:52.923
Princess Ding has arrived.

40:07.363 --> 40:08.843
How dare you to come back?

40:10.883 --> 40:12.242
Why wouldn't I dare to come back?

40:14.162 --> 40:15.632
You ungrateful wretch!

40:15.632 --> 40:17.904
You caused your grandmother's death,
violating human ethics,

40:17.904 --> 40:19.280
unacceptable by both moral and law.

40:19.280 --> 40:21.642
How dare you to stand before her coffin?

40:22.843 --> 40:24.042
I caused her death?

40:26.162 --> 40:29.242
Father, you were also
in the courtyard that night.

40:29.963 --> 40:31.363
You saw it with your own eyes.

40:31.883 --> 40:35.803
That night, a thunderbolt struck down
a tree and hit Grandmother,

40:36.003 --> 40:37.522
causing her severe injuries and death.

40:38.283 --> 40:41.323
This is a natural disaster.
What does it have to do with me?

40:49.122 --> 40:51.763
Father, say something.

40:52.363 --> 40:53.162
Ye Li!

40:54.923 --> 40:56.403
You ungrateful wretch!

40:56.803 --> 40:59.323
I will now punish you
on behalf of the ancestors.

40:59.883 --> 41:00.682
I...

41:00.763 --> 41:01.883
- Wending!
- I...

41:01.883 --> 41:03.403
This is a funeral hall.

41:03.843 --> 41:06.242
Let Mom leave in peace.

41:06.443 --> 41:08.443
A false charge needs no true reason.

41:09.363 --> 41:12.522
What now? Uncle Wending,
do you want to kill me

41:12.592 --> 41:13.602
to avenge Grandmother?

41:13.602 --> 41:15.202
Just stop it.

41:15.522 --> 41:16.803
- Move!
- I...

41:16.803 --> 41:17.602
How dare you!

41:19.082 --> 41:20.682
After all, you are an official.

41:20.682 --> 41:23.122
The Ye family is a scholarly
and upright household.

41:23.202 --> 41:24.722
You should be well-versed in the laws.

41:25.642 --> 41:28.323
If you have evidence, report it
to Jingzhao Prefecture for a trial.

41:28.323 --> 41:29.202
If not,

41:29.363 --> 41:31.763
stop slandering an innocent person
with a false charge.

41:40.843 --> 41:42.242
Do you have anything else to say?

41:43.363 --> 41:47.323
If not, I'll see Grandmother off
for the last time.

42:15.363 --> 42:16.602
The gods

42:17.803 --> 42:18.963
bear witness above.

42:22.704 --> 42:24.912
(Preview)

42:25.562 --> 42:26.923
I want you to take a walk with me.

42:27.642 --> 42:28.443
Take a walk?

42:29.642 --> 42:30.883
I'm a cripple.

42:31.162 --> 42:32.003
Then I'll push you.

42:32.722 --> 42:33.403
Alright.

42:36.363 --> 42:39.522
If you stand up, you can try
to take a couple of steps forward.

42:50.003 --> 42:51.843
I never thought I could stand up again.

42:53.443 --> 42:54.843
You healed my legs.

42:56.042 --> 42:56.923
Li.

42:58.483 --> 42:59.363
Thank you.

43:00.483 --> 43:02.562
How many more times
will you say thank you?

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
♪Unbound by form♪
